{
  "stem": "24958.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there was a beautiful sewing machine-- a Pfaff sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a ball.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I sewed all these things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I made some brassieres, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for-- for skirts, kerchiefs, because we didn't had no hair, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there were curtains, bedspreads-- whatever I could cut off there, I will.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there, I know you told us that you got-- that-- took the horse-- stole the horse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We wanted to go to the-- there was no train, because the tracks were-- this section was bombed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It couldn't be no train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the way-- on the way in--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Krakow, we are-- I went back to-- to-- to this-- when I was before, when the war broke on, I was in a furnished room with my husband and with my child.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went back to this lady, which-- so I said to her, look.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But would you give me this one room?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had two rooms in this thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Give me one room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know I am a dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm gonna make some money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm gonna pay you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I stayed in this room there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then-- then a friend of mine moved in with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was also a dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we started to sew-- you know, we started to make a-- earn ourself a living so we could go to a bath, you know, we could take care of ourselves a little bit.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, after maybe that we were liberated in May-- that must have been in-- in-- we were there till September, I think.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In September, there came a-- a newspaper in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
